"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/19/0300-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-19 03:00#[feature] LLM Council Skill Implemented: The LLM Council skill has been implemented, providing a robust framework for analyzing complex questions. This skill leverages a council of five distinct AI advisors, each with a unique perspective (Contrarian, First Principles Thinker, Expansionist, Outsider, and a Chairman for synthesis). The purpose is to pressure-test ideas, decisions, and questions by exposing them to diverse viewpoints and critical peer review, ultimately leading to a more comprehensive and well-reasoned final recommendation. This is particularly valuable for high-stakes decisions where the cost of error is significant.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"z2wm35","at":1782088668456},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.09900138,-0.00466805,0.04619315,-0.04225611,-0.03675241,0.00855854,0.01584021,0.00688018,0.03035821,-0.06488156,0.04068382,-0.01736447,0.01972628,0.05483403,-0.00381501,0.03981752,-0.03341257,0.01083239,0.06406869,0.03652038,0.05095853,-0.03075189,0.01536163,0.00523494,-0.01851875,0.01075803,-0.0361739,-0.09286132,-0.08363029,-0.2317269,0.04403925,0.00059323,0.06816296,-0.01148201,-0.04940107,-0.05376448,-0.07482488,0.02206351,-0.03965839,0.05416373,0.00396451,-0.03828346,-0.00283408,-0.04674047,-0.01933187,-0.05574411,-0.02824282,-0.0473864,-0.07319661,-0.0175539,-0.07903249,-0.05346118,0.00576389,-0.00460136,0.04425275,0.05097413,0.02161945,0.01812754,0.04598736,0.10765672,0.06735883,0.05120052,-0.23175892,0.10055962,0.01018684,0.04214198,-0.02779983,0.04305933,0.05801669,0.04583216,-0.01389087,-0.03829955,0.07651916,0.03562418,0.05939279,0.01606916,-0.01125512,-0.0155493,0.04047053,-0.03215257,0.00736211,0.03400421,0.00121925,-0.09721322,-0.01101202,-0.04242385,-0.02534146,0.0184956,0.01550954,0.00887785,0.01669211,0.04502341,-0.07381625,0.0334507,-0.0299133,-0.02447167,0.01692118,-0.02849814,-0.11648357,0.13654593,-0.03168762