"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/19/0300-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-19 03:00#[feature] LLM Council Skill: The LLM Council skill has been implemented to enhance decision-making processes. This skill operates by routing user queries through a simulated council of five AI advisors, each with a unique analytical lens. The advisors include a Contrarian (focusing on flaws), a First Principles Thinker (re-evaluating the core problem), an Expansionist (seeking upside), and an Outsider (providing an unbiased view). This multi-faceted approach ensures that questions are thoroughly examined from various angles, leading to more robust and well-considered outcomes. The skill is intended for situations where the cost of a wrong decision is high, offering a structured way to gain diverse insights before committing to a course of action.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"vxaz81","at":1782088668962},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.07667691,-0.02011697,0.06220992,-0.03457105,-0.03286653,0.02584584,0.03033175,0.01569713,0.02083157,-0.0442307,0.02958762,-0.01182131,0.02154037,0.05778387,-0.00377624,0.0458882,-0.0492596,0.03290389,0.06702497,0.02873374,0.04073242,-0.02989697,0.01924943,0.00522103,0.0052126,-0.00612218,-0.03041602,-0.0800826,-0.07564613,-0.21392894,0.04405428,0.01476666,0.05428322,-0.00630216,-0.0717786,-0.04874862,-0.09348387,0.0566215,-0.0426572,0.06190329,0.0038074,-0.05619876,-0.01065865,-0.04990495,-0.03226828,-0.05760466,-0.00845708,-0.05563586,-0.05250376,-0.04095047,-0.09472859,-0.07138076,-0.00898373,-0.01653688,0.04955548,0.02414997,0.0367958,0.03486896,0.04366742,0.08515191,0.0562254,0.04460488,-0.22029622,0.09924833,-0.00277844,0.03376119,-0.03105678,0.03015846,0.06186251,0.03347277,-0.02931902,-0.03765859,0.06205371,0.01540913,0.05937127,-0.00359465,-0.01826715,-0.00775919,0.03019499,-0.01731596,0.00702904,0.03738752,0.00016296,-0.08244618,0.00616767,-0.04116613,-0.04210546,0.01560248,0.02248337,0.01342837,0.03646247,