"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/19/0300-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-19 03:00#[discovery] npm network access and mermaid-cli installation check yielded no output: Several commands were executed to diagnose potential issues with `npm` network access and the installation of `mermaid-cli`. These included checking the `mermaid` package version via `npm view`, listing contents of the `~/.npm/_npx` directory, and searching the filesystem for the `mmdc` executable. Despite these attempts, none of the commands produced any output on either stdout or stderr. This lack of information makes it impossible to determine if `npm` has network access, if `mermaid-cli` is installed in the expected location, or if the executable is present elsewhere on the system.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1glq4o2","at":1782088669005},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.07702478,-0.02697302,0.06449738,-0.02989494,0.03588965,-0.00459849,-0.01921608,0.02544156,-0.00764073,-0.00493088,0.05095132,-0.04884123,0.04327884,0.03061885,0.01635627,-0.00443612,-0.00829808,-0.04626248,0.11448491,0.00355859,0.03644044,-0.03051919,-0.00660363,-0.02741136,-0.02547993,0.09568577,0.02001236,-0.04921722,-0.07270867,-0.23765071,-0.02969805,0.00699407,0.04610877,-0.01929827,0.03114298,-0.00861456,-0.03892076,-0.00557549,0.00046119,0.01931786,-0.01127552,-0.02000951,-0.00107924,-0.00382864,-0.03185936,-0.06666901,0.0055629,-0.02322533,0.02293306,-0.07012784,-0.02561481,-0.02836982,0.07815861,-0.02580128,0.01413582,0.05968576,0.00550911,0.03681428,0.02141679,0.07815886,0.04199141,0.03497879,-0.19813859,0.04838489,0.1061637,0.04181259,-0.00975315,-0.03448203,0.07053148,-0.01091356,-0.03404168,-0.03264954,-0.02348896,0.03604403,0.05129853,0.00139713,0.01331102,-0.04160627,-0.00992501,-0.03566432,-0.02697499,-0.00425674,0.01617269,-0.0373428,0.00911179,-0.01203609,-0.00333904,0.07006884,0.03015576,-0.0002115,-0.03866395,-0.03757175,-0.02100714,0.0620291,-0.08865032,0.08559858,0.08120