"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/19/0300-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-19 03:00#[feature] LLM Council Skill Implemented: The LLM Council skill has been implemented to enhance decision-making processes. This skill leverages a methodology adapted from Andrej Karpathy's LLM Council, employing five independent AI advisors, each with a unique thinking lens. These advisors include the Contrarian (focuses on flaws), the First Principles Thinker (strips down to core problems), the Expansionist (identifies upside and adjacent opportunities), and the Outsider (provides an unbiased perspective). The process involves independent analysis by each advisor, followed by peer review and synthesis into a final recommendation. This is particularly valuable for decisions where the cost of being wrong is high, offering a robust way to explore different angles and mitigate risks.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1sn76m","at":1782088669242},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.07743517,-0.02089984,0.05415624,-0.04058848,-0.04416805,0.00330701,0.0168549,0.01260476,0.0370727,-0.0664095,0.04314846,0.00013389,0.02197058,0.05203332,0.00890832,0.03417251,-0.05180427,0.03725397,0.05443352,0.03256674,0.04068343,-0.04952833,0.02180905,0.01709423,0.01021237,-0.00607367,-0.03882688,-0.07772762,-0.07774913,-0.22466385,0.05880636,0.01672079,0.04484173,-0.02118115,-0.06853881,-0.03617167,-0.090937,0.04702245,-0.03875127,0.0377284,-0.016779,-0.04778367,-0.01788116,-0.04894328,-0.02858767,-0.07563318,-0.01454277,-0.05239014,-0.06627071,-0.01791477,-0.06835591,-0.0531288,0.00335728,-0.00866308,0.03441942,0.02721234,0.03422278,0.03261581,0.04319712,0.08066265,0.04874434,0.05181094,-0.22840257,0.10203219,-0.00599392,0.04590166,-0.03829912,0.03386359,0.07020071,0.04204362,-0.03090024,-0.01348393,0.05246851,0.00467119,0.06233009,0.00114048,-0.01810254,-0.00936229,0.02703432,-0.01542747,0.01980336,0.05679528,-0.00867805,-0.09142233,-0.00364189,-0.05447278,-0.04296703,-0.000612